skin_overrides.change_skin.message: This will change your skin for all players.
skin_overrides.change_skin.message.vanil: This will change your skin for all players, including those not on the server. Your updated skin will only show for other players when you leave and rejoin. If skin overrides is installed on the server, changes will be instant.
skin_overrides.change_skin.message.modde: This will change your skin for all players, and everyone online will see the update immediately. You can use a library override if you want to change your skin for server players only.
